//  in <c>catalogs/mclaren.json</c> +
//  <c>catalogs/dtc-mclaren.json</c>. McLaren's MSO toolchain is
//  in-house; the catalogue documents the consumer-reachable UDS
//  surface only.
//
//  Seed-key starter is the KWP2000 two's-complement; production
//  callers register the real MSO algorithm via RegisterAlgorithm.
